window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Hoist the black flag and prepare the spell cannons!</p> <p>Jon, Lilly, and the crew, must pick up the pieces after their last battle, and travel to the heart of the Illuminous Empire to take on the mad emperor! Will they be able to hold their family and crew together as they face impossible odds? Can they free the peoples and island nations of Aquris from a monster's iron grip?</p> <p><i>My Girlfriends are Pirate Elves! </i>is a fun, sexy, adventurous story of a nautical nature. It contains humor, outlandish adventure, lewd acts, dreadful strategies, a Deep One, secrets revealed, pointed ears, magical pistols, sharp teeth, holy might, and there might be a flying automaton somewhere in there. </p> <p>This story is for mature listeners 18 and up. </p> <p>Avast! There be elves in these waters!</p>"; 
